headline.print_headline: High Unemployment Still Haunting Military Veterans
headline.main: High Unemployment Still Haunting Military Veterans

lead_paragraph: Unemployment among U.S. military veterans eased last year, government data showed on Thursday, but remained far higher than the national average rate for the civilian population.
